  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个FinTech系统的架构图，核心是LedgerService作为用户入口，然后经过DNS解析到CDN层，最后落到存储。先确认一下整体结构？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白，LedgerService作为入口节点，然后分三层：DNS层、CDN层、存储层。我先把USER节点和三个subgraph画出来，命名分别是DNS、CDN、STORAGE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "DNS",
        "CDN",
        "STORAGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "DNS层里面放Route 53，但这里我们内部代号叫PaymentGateway。CDN层比较复杂，需要包含Edge节点、Lambda@Edge、证书管理和缓存四个组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在DNS subgraph里放了R53节点，CDN subgraph里放了EDGE、LAMBDA、CERT、CACHE四个节点。存储层需要放OAI和文件存储对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，存储层是OAI和FILES，其中FILES对应TransactionQueue。不过有个问题——我刚才说的命名需要统一，所有节点都要用FinTech的业务命名，比如R53实际是FinTech_PaymentGateway。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "FILES"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "收到，我修正一下显示文本。R53显示为FinTech_PaymentGateway，EDGE显示为FinTech_LedgerService，LAMBDA也是FinTech_PaymentGateway，CERT是FinTech_FraudDetection，CACHE回到FinTech_LedgerService，OAI是FinTech_PaymentGateway，FILES是FinTech_TransactionQueue。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "R53",
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE",
        "OAI",
        "FILES",
        "USER"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "现在画连接关系。用户通过HTTPS访问，先到R53，然后流量进入EDGE节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：USER到R53的HTTPS连接，以及R53到EDGE的无标签连接。接下来EDGE到LAMBDA？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "USER",
        "R53",
        "EDGE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，EDGE触发Lambda@Edge处理，然后Lambda去验证CERT证书，证书验证通过后操作CACHE缓存。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
        "LAMBDA",
        "CERT",
        "CACHE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已连接EDGE→LAMBDA→CERT→CACHE。缓存之后到存储层，这里有什么特殊要求吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "EDGE",
